TopicTitle: KSO Shuttle Missions: STS 102 Spy Satellite and Crew Transfer to Space Station

Articles.Content:
The Second of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions! STS 102's objectives are to bring up a spy satellite and perform a crew transfer at the Kerbal Space Station.

Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 103 Will bring a munar landing probe into low Kerbin orbit before returning to the KSC!
